introduction: This video provides an overview of artificial intelligence (AI), machine learning (ML), and deep learning (DL), their differences, and examples of their applications. The speaker covers the basics of AI, including Amazon Echo, and explains how machine learning and deep learning are subcategories of AI. The video also discusses the types of AI, such as supervised learning, and provides examples of each. Lastly, the speaker touches on the future of AI and its potential impact on various industries.
